 "Excellent Cyngar. I almost forgot how clever you could be." He turned to 
storm. "I know you can do this. I think its best you keep your memory, I need 
you to remmeber always where your loyalty is. Do not dissapoint me you have 
so much potential. Now go and get in ur pod. We'll launch you far out of 
thier sensors so they cant tell u didnt fall from space.   You'll then land 
safely infront of the tripred base and get rescuded. Just make the black 
light go around to make it look like ur scanning for a beast mode. Quilldart 
over there is installing a cover signal so all theyd be able to trace is a 
protoform until ur ready to get out. Whenever ur ready my little temptress."

--part1_5a.e265435.2a5e7af1_boundary
